<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Registro propietario KYC - TaxiGE</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        * { box-sizing:border-box; }
        body {
            margin:0;
            font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
            background:#f3f6fb;
            color:#111827;
        }
        .hero {
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 15% 10%, rgba(245,158,11,.25), transparent 28%),
                linear-gradient(135deg,#020617,#111827);
            color:white;
            padding:30px 20px 70px;
        }
        .hero-inner {
            width:min(1120px,100%);
            margin:0 auto;
        }
        .brand {
            display:flex;
            align-items:center;
            gap:12px;
            font-weight:900;
            font-size:22px;
            margin-bottom:54px;
        }
        .logo {
            width:44px;
            height:44px;
            border-radius:15px;
            background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f59e0b,#facc15);
            color:#111827;
            display:flex;
            align-items:center;
            justify-content:center;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,58px);
            margin:0 0 12px;
            letter-spacing:-.05em;
        }
        .hero p {
            color:#cbd5e1;
            font-size:18px;
            max-width:760px;
            line-height:1.7;
        }
        .container {
            width:min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
            margin:-44px auto 60px;
        }
        .card {
            background:white;
            border-radius:28px;
            padding:28px;
            box-shadow:0 24px 70px rgba(15,23,42,.18);
        }
        .section-title {
            margin:22px 0 14px;
            padding:12px 14px;
            border-radius:16px;
            background:#f8fafc;
            font-weight:900;
            color:#334155;
        }
        .grid {
            display:grid;
            grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
            gap:16px;
        }
        label {
            display:block;
            font-weight:900;
            margin-bottom:7px;
            font-size:14px;
        }
        input, select, textarea {
            width:100%;
            padding:14px;
            border:1px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius:14px;
            background:#f8fafc;
        }
        input:focus, textarea:focus {
            outline:3px solid rgba(245,158,11,.22);
            border-color:#f59e0b;
            background:white;
        }
        .error {
            color:#991b1b;
            font-size:13px;
            margin-top:6px;
            font-weight:700;
        }
        .notice {
            background:#fef3c7;
            color:#92400e;
            border-radius:16px;
            padding:14px;
            font-weight:800;
            margin-bottom:18px;
        }
        .submit {
            width:100%;
            margin-top:24px;
            padding:16px;
            border:0;
            border-radius:16px;
            background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f59e0b,#facc15);
            color:#111827;
            font-weight:900;
            cursor:pointer;
            font-size:16px;
        }
        @media(max-width:760px) {
            .grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
            .card { padding:20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="brand"><div class="logo">TG</div>TaxiGE Platform</div>
        <h1>Solicitud de propietario de taxi</h1>
        <p>Completa tus datos personales, documentos KYC y documentos del taxi. Tu cuenta quedará pendiente hasta que el superusuario revise y apruebe la solicitud.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="container">
    <div class="card">
        <div class="notice">
            Importante: enviar esta solicitud no activa el panel automáticamente. TaxiGE revisará tu identidad y los documentos del taxi.
        </div>

        <form method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            {% csrf_token %}

            {% if form.non_field_errors %}
                {% for error in form.non_field_errors %}
                    <div class="error">{{ error }}</div>
                {% endfor %}
            {% endif %}

            <div class="section-title">1. Datos de cuenta</div>
            <div class="grid">
                {% for name in "username,email,password,password_confirm,first_name,last_name,user_phone"|cut:" " %}
                {% endfor %}
            </div>

            <div class="grid">
                <div><label>{{ form.username.label }}</label>{{ form.username }}{% for e in form.username.errors %}<div class="error">{{ e }}</div>{% endfor %}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.email.label }}</label>{{ form.email }}{% for e in form.email.errors %}<div class="error">{{ e }}</div>{% endfor %}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.password.label }}</label>{{ form.password }}{% for e in form.password.errors %}<div class="error">{{ e }}</div>{% endfor %}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.password_confirm.label }}</label>{{ form.password_confirm }}{% for e in form.password_confirm.errors %}<div class="error">{{ e }}</div>{% endfor %}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.first_name.label }}</label>{{ form.first_name }}{% for e in form.first_name.errors %}<div class="error">{{ e }}</div>{% endfor %}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.last_name.label }}</label>{{ form.last_name }}{% for e in form.last_name.errors %}<div class="error">{{ e }}</div>{% endfor %}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.user_phone.label }}</label>{{ form.user_phone }}{% for e in form.user_phone.errors %}<div class="error">{{ e }}</div>{% endfor %}</div>
            </div>

            <div class="section-title">2. Identificación del propietario</div>
            <div class="grid">
                <div><label>{{ form.owner_full_name.label }}</label>{{ form.owner_full_name }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.phone.label }}</label>{{ form.phone }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.city.label }}</label>{{ form.city }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.address.label }}</label>{{ form.address }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.identity_number.label }}</label>{{ form.identity_number }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.identity_document.label }}</label>{{ form.identity_document }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.selfie_photo.label }}</label>{{ form.selfie_photo }}</div>
            </div>

            <div class="section-title">3. Empresa o flota</div>
            <div class="grid">
                <div><label>{{ form.company_name.label }}</label>{{ form.company_name }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.taxi_count.label }}</label>{{ form.taxi_count }}</div>
            </div>

            <div class="section-title">4. Taxi principal de verificación</div>
            <div class="grid">
                <div><label>{{ form.main_taxi_brand.label }}</label>{{ form.main_taxi_brand }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.main_taxi_model.label }}</label>{{ form.main_taxi_model }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.main_taxi_plate.label }}</label>{{ form.main_taxi_plate }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.main_taxi_color.label }}</label>{{ form.main_taxi_color }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.taxi_registration_document.label }}</label>{{ form.taxi_registration_document }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.taxi_license_document.label }}</label>{{ form.taxi_license_document }}</div>
                <div><label>{{ form.ownership_proof_document.label }}</label>{{ form.ownership_proof_document }}</div>
            </div>

            <div class="section-title">5. Mensaje adicional</div>
            <div>
                <label>{{ form.message.label }}</label>
                {{ form.message }}
            </div>

            <button class="submit" type="submit">Enviar solicitud KYC</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
